 [K:E]_s = [K:F]_s$. See also `Module.finrank_mul_finrank`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/FieldTheory/SeparableDegree.html#Field.finSepDegree_mul_finSepDegree_of_isAlgebraic","kind":"theorem","line":278,"name":"Field.finSepDegree_mul_finSepDegree_of_isAlgebraic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/FieldTheory/SeparableDegree.lean#L278-L285"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/FieldTheory/SeparableDegree.html#Field.finSepDegree_eq_zero_of_transcendental\"><span class=\"name\">Field</span>.<span class=\"name\">finSepDegree_eq_zero_of_transcendental</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">F</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">F</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Algebraic/Defs.html#Algebra.Transcendental\">Algebra.Transcendental</a> <span class=\"fn\">F</span> <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><spa